Problem Link : https://leetcode.com/problems/add-digits/description/

Java Solution:

class Solution {
    public int addDigits(int num) {
        if(num == 0) 
        return 0;
        else if(num % 9 == 0) 
        return 9;
        else 
        return num % 9;
    }
}

C++ Solution:

class Solution {
public:
    int addDigits(int num) {
         if(num == 0) 
        return 0;
        else if(num % 9 == 0) 
        return 9;
        else 
        return num % 9;
    }
};
